ZID Proxy - SNI-based Transparent HTTPS Proxy for pfSense

This package provides a transparent proxy for HTTPS traffic that performs
dual-factor filtering based on source IP address and destination hostname
(extracted from TLS SNI extension without terminating TLS).

Features:
- Transparent HTTPS proxy (port 443)
- SNI hostname extraction without TLS termination
- IP/CIDR-based source filtering
- Wildcard hostname matching (*.example.com)
- ALLOW/BLOCK rules with ALLOW priority
- Runtime rule reloading via SIGHUP
- Detailed connection logging
- pfSense web interface integration

WWW: https://github.com/guilherme/zid-proxy
